name: WATERCOLOR PAPER - The little lighthouse theater
description:
Print of my illustration "The little lighthouse theater".
The original is an digital illustration.
Printed on an 250g Fine Art Watercolor Paper, Letter format.
Free of acid - Optical brightener - Neutral PH.
The image is centered on the paper.
Signed and dated by me on the front.
Copyright will not appear on your print.
I always mention "DO NOT BEND PLEASE" on my packages, and ship in Priority airmail.

Please convo me for any questions.

© 2010 Sandrine Mercier ♥
All my work are not royalty-free

With a lot of wishes,
